{"tid":1204918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衝鋒隊警員中環執勤　遺失警察通訊器","createTime":"2019-06-11T16:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T16:32:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"168c42f40e0aa0ba8d20795d275edc51346f92ee","tid":1204918,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"一名隸屬港島總區衝鋒隊的警務人員昨日（10日）凌晨1時許在中環添美道執勤期間，意外遺失一部警察通訊器，警方接獲遺失器材的報告後，立即展開調查及到現場搜尋，暫未有發現，案件列作「遺失政府財物」，由港島總區人員跟進調查，有關警察通訊器已停用及失效。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民如拾獲該警察通訊器，應立即把通訊器交到就近的警署，或致電28601060與調查人員聯絡。"},{"pid":"a0655e82836f1eb14611fedd4f1ff92c1292f91c","tid":1204918,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190611/59704965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F59704965&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TidUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=a7f54e23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F59704965&h=e8defda4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190611/59704965</a>"},{"pid":"efc91eaebb72c6430ef7cc3d1c07b9587de6c46c","tid":1204918,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"有嘢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}